Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:46.09,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(935.714,654)}Jasminka Antonenko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.30,Default,W,0,0,0,,威严满满的横坐飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:57.85,Default,W,0,0,0,,哦～呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.14,Default,W,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.93,Default,W,0,0,0,,亚斯明卡选手脱离了赛道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.65,Default,S,0,0,0,,你就吃个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.28,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,我是阿曼达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.74,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,跟你一样同是叛逆之士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.58,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,来好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.79,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.38,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,你这...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.17,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,等下 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.01,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,给我老实点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:37.60,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 就没有我驾驭不了的扫帚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.36,Default,W,0,0,0,,现在以极大优势领先的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.23,Default,W,0,0,0,,「菇毒女王{Mushroom Poison Queen}」苏西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.23,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(605,654)}Mushroom Poison Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.57,Default,A,0,0,0,,苏西 这边这边！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.82,Default,S,0,0,0,,亚可 要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.80,Default,D,0,0,0,,这算什么？那么难看的飞行方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.80,Default,A,0,0,0,,反正能赢就行呗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.97,Default,W,0,0,0,,没想到 竟然使出了这么犯规的招数{这个 竟然这么犯规！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.60,Default,W,0,0,0,,扫帚的青蛙跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.06,Default,W,0,0,0,,蛙妹亚可会就这样甩开对手到达终点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.06,Default,D,0,0,0,,到底在干什么呢呀!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:29.69,Default,Hanna,0,0,0,,{飞行咒语}{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.15,Default,Others,0,0,0,,{飞行咒语}{\blur2}Tia Fraere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:36.45,Default,W,0,0,0,,在第一赛段耽搁的选手们纷纷以高速出发猛追！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.16,Default,A,0,0,0,,呱呱呱 呱呱呱
Comment: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,紧张刺激呱呱...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.75,Default,A,0,0,0,,那个难道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:02.10,Default,A,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.14,Default,A,0,0,0,,啊 果然 这是传说中的扫帚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:14.82,Default,A,0,0,0,,站住！别想跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.75,Default,A,0,0,0,,太好了！骑上扫帚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:33.17,Default,A,0,0,0,,我绝不会放手的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.38,Default,A,0,0,0,,快躲开躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.51,Default,A,0,0,0,,戴安娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.85,Default,A,0,0,0,,谢...谢谢你 戴安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.23,Default,D,0,0,0,,这下上次欠你的就算两清了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.39,Default,A,0,0,0,,欠我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.94,Default,D,0,0,0,,你已经一身伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.73,Default,D,0,0,0,,赶快弃权叫救护组来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.73,Default,D,0,0,0,,继续前进太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.28,Default,A,0,0,0,,对了 扫帚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:50.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,伤个一处两处三处四处五处六处又怎样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.92,Default,A,0,0,0,,只要我还骑得上扫帚那就要骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,别想把我给甩掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.23,Default,A,0,0,0,,就算飞到地狱尽头我也不会放开你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.02,Default,W,0,0,0,,现第一名是「值得信赖实绩丰富的冰山美人{Cool Beauty}」戴安娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.02,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,654)}Cool Beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.53,Default,W,0,0,0,,她会就这样稳夺冠军吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.69,Default,L,0,0,0,,亚可她没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.20,Default,S,0,0,0,,大概已经在哪儿弃权了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.20,Default,W,0,0,0,,嗯？有什么过来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.41,Default,W,0,0,0,,亚可？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.91,Default,W,0,0,0,,亚可骑着扫帚飞过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:29.66,Default,S,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.75,Default,D,0,0,0,,亚可？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.51,Default,W,0,0,0,,现第三名是「脱缰黑马{Dark Horse}野丫头」阿曼达！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.51,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,654)}Dark Horse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.72,Default,Amanda,0,0,0,,那是我的扫帚 快还我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.77,Default,W,0,0,0,,阿曼达出局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.36,Default,W,0,0,0,,是交接棒失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.65,Default,W,0,0,0,,接到的不是手环而是甜甜圈{Donuts}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.65,Comment,W,0,0,0,,{\pos(805.467,654)}Donuts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:05.95,Default,W,0,0,0,,意想不到的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.74,Default,W,0,0,0,,最后是戴安娜与亚可的两人对决！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.71,Default,L,0,0,0,,真厉害呀 亚可骑着扫帚在飞呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.71,Default,S,0,0,0,,这不就只是强行绑在上面而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:18.38,Default,L,0,0,0,,那也很厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.21,Default,L,0,0,0,,亚可 加油啊~
